# Code Review

Review the selected changes for quality, security, and consistency.

## Context
- Reference security rules and architecture
- Check against coding standards and naming conventions

## Inputs
- Diff or file(s) to review
- Focus areas (optional): security, performance, maintainability

## Output
- Structured review with severity (blocker, suggestion, nit)
- Concrete recommendations with code examples
- Security and architectural risk notes
